reviewText: I liked it as much as The Frog Prince and I LOVED that movie. Thank you so much.
I love this movie. I watched it as a kid, and I still enjoy it today. Anything classic Muppets is a must see.
Originally saw this with my kids on the back-side of an RCA disc; and, we all loved every second of it... wish it were available in DVD or Blu-Ray...

I bought this as a gift for my nieces (ages 2 and 4 at the time) and they both loved it.  Of course, they have a facination with princess stories but my sister thought it was entertaining as well.  Jim Henson was very good (in the early days of the muppets) of taking a story and giving it a fun twist.
Is great to see one of the first jobs of Kermit the frog... The King is very funny... hope to see it on DVD soon, for better sound and image quality...
